{"id":1173,"date":"2025-04-05T00:16:41","date_gmt":"2025-04-04T17:16:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1173"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:41:08","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:41:08","slug":"vi-kim-cang-bong","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/vi-kim-cang-bong\/","title":{"rendered":"Vi kim c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh cho da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1, da nh\u0103n n\u00f4ng, da s\u1ea7n v\u1ecf cam, s\u1ea1m m\u00e0u, mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1eadt tone c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 sau 60 ph\u00fat<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>B\u1eadt t\u1eeb 2-3 tone sau 1 bu\u1ed5i li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh<\/li>\n<li>Da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng, thu nh\u1ecf l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng<\/li>\n<li>Tr\u1ebb h\u00f3a da- gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n n\u00f4ng,da c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>V\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p thay da sinh h\u1ecdc, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb tinh th\u1ec3 b\u1ee5i m\u1ecbn vi kim c\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf da ch\u1ebft, t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2u d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u1ebf b\u00e0o bong tr\u00f3c, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u00e0n da m\u1edbi, mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng kho\u1ebb m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da duy tr\u00ec t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi Dr.Leemee k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa hai c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7: C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt qu\u00fd gi\u00e1( S\u00e2m n\u00fai, h\u1ea3i s\u00e2m, tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 t\u1ea7m \u0111en) v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 l\u00ean men mang l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1, c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb 1 &#8211; 2 ti\u1ebfng<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 03 \u2013 05 l\u1ea7n, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n kho\u1ea3ng 21 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -26px; top: 392.563px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh cho da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1, da nh\u0103n n\u00f4ng, da s\u1ea7n v\u1ecf cam, s\u1ea1m m\u00e0u, mang \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1eadt tone c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ec9 sau 60 ph\u00fat<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3715,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[34],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1173","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-microneedling","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1173","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1173"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3715"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1173"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=1173"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","emb